WEBVTT

00:01:28.951 --> 00:01:30.101
(Deflating sound)

00:01:30.125 --> 00:01:31.309
(Laughter)

00:01:31.333 --> 00:01:34.018
My mentor was conducting
clown rounds in the hospital

00:01:34.042 --> 00:01:35.684
when he was approached by a nurse.

00:01:35.708 --> 00:01:37.893
They needed to put a tube
up the kid's nose.

00:01:37.917 --> 00:01:39.184
Kid didn't want to do it,

00:01:39.208 --> 00:01:40.809
so rather than hold the kid down,

00:01:40.833 --> 00:01:42.786
they asked my colleague if he could help.

00:01:42.810 --> 00:01:45.101
So the clown asked for a second tube

00:01:45.125 --> 00:01:47.268
and shoved it up his own nose.

00:01:47.292 --> 00:01:48.542
Kid of like this.

00:01:49.583 --> 00:01:51.792
Oh, please don't do this at home.

00:01:58.875 --> 00:02:00.059
(Laughter)